name: cloud-meta
description: This set of APIs provides a way to view cloud providers and regions.

name: cluster-operations
description: This set of APIs provides a way to manage Zilliz Cloud clusters in a cloud provider.

name: collection-operations
description: This set of APIs provides a way to manage collections in Zilliz Cloud.

name: import-operations
description: This set of APIs provides a way to import data into Zilliz Cloud.

name: pipeline-operations
description: This set of APIs provides a way to manage Zilliz Cloud Pipelines.

name: vector-operations
description: This set of APIs provides a way to perform CRUD operations on the data stored in Zilliz Cloud.
